Class AbstractBoard

java.lang.Object
HW7.AbstractBoard

public abstract class AbstractBoard

    • Equals

      public boolean Equals​(AbstractBoard other)
      If two board configuration are the same it returns 1, otherwise returns 0.

      It does not compare last move , number of moves done by user

      Parameters:
      other - Other board that will compared to
      Returns:
      If two board configuration are the same it returns true, otherwise returns false. It does not compare last move and number of moves done by user
